---
import "./learn-belay.scss";
import Frame from "../../layouts/frame.astro";
import Accordian from "../../components/Accordian.astro";
import Qa from "../../components/parts/Qa.astro";
---

<Frame
    title={" - London Coaching"}
    description={"Coaching is now available at Vauxwall East. Hayden has been coaching climbing for 5 years and is a qualified coach. If you're looking to learn technique or push your grade, he’d love to help."}
>
    <div class="seshpage card">
        <h1>Private Coaching - London</h1>
        <div class="seshpage-options">
            <div class="img-li">
                <img
                    class="seshpage-img square-img"
                    src="/media/coaching.jpg"
                    alt="Hayden is climbing on an overhanging bouldering wall, using just his finger tips on the small crimps."
                />
                <ul>
                    <li>Technique & Physical Training</li>
                    <li>Long & Short Term Coaching</li>
                    <li>Weekly Remote Support</li>
                    <li>A Wide Range of Resources</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="seshpage-info flex">
                <p>
                    We are now offering private coaching sessions at Vauxwall
                    West. These sessions aimed towards beginner & intermediate
                    climbers below the V6 grade.<br />
                    You’ll be coached around your style of climbing, the adjustments
                    made should feel natural and efficient. Coaching is a journey,
                    we are looking to get climbers to their goals, so if your looking
                    for continued support or direction, this is a great opportunity.<br
                    /> If you have a climbing partner, we recommend 2:1 coaching
                    and having booking 2 sessions back to back.
                </p>
                <strong
                    >You’ll need to bring your own equipment and pay for your
                    entry.</strong
                >
            </div>
            <div class="seshpage-buttons">
                <script
                    is:inline
                    src="https://assets.ticketinghub.com/checkout.js"
                    data-widget="158f5c03-eb1b-4fb5-9542-c620dcc77410"
                    data-ga-track-pageviews="false"
                ></script> - More dates released soon!
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <Accordian>
        <Qa question="Where will I meet my coach?">
            Hayden will be at reception at the start of your session. If you
            haven't been to a London Climbing Centre wall yet, please fill out
            the waiver online to save time."
        </Qa>
        <Qa question="Can I be coached at other centres?">
            Yes, please get in touch as we may be able to coach at your local
            centre.
        </Qa>
        <Qa question="Other Queries?">
            Please send us your queries, send an <a
                href="mailto:hayden@southsideclimbing.co.uk">email</a
            > or fill out the form on our <a href="/contact/">contact page.</a>
        </Qa>
    </Accordian>
</Frame>
